block content
  .o-section.u-height--100.u-background--text-1
    .u-height--100.u-1-of-1
      .o-wrapper.u-height--100.u-max-width--1024
        .o-box
          .o-box__stuff
            .c-logo
              img(src="/images/hoho.png", alt="Hoho Challenge" class="u-max-width--600")
            .u-1-of-1
              .text
                p
                  | The challenge of the week is to design a  
                  
                  span#selection-enviroment(class='box') 
                    

                  | that deals with  
                  
                  span#selection-object-one(class='box')
                    
                
                  | and contains

                  span#selection-object-two(class='box')
                    
            br
            br
            .u-1-of-1
              a(href="#subscribe", class='btn-more')
                | Subscribe, It's Free !!

            .u-1-of-1    
              div.you-dare
                div 
                  img(src="/images/suspect.png", alt="Suspect")
                div.you-dare-text
                  | YOU DARE

  .o-section.u-height--100.u-background--secondary
    .u-height--100.u-1-of-1
      .o-wrapper.u-height--100.u-max-width--800
        .c-title
          | Challenge 
          span.c-text-color-pink
            | rules

        .c-rules-list 
          ul
            li
              .c-rule
                | Design something creative according to the weekly draw.
            li
              .c-rule
                | When you have your design soon, publish a tweet with the hashtag 
                a.a-subscribe(href='https://twitter.com/search?src=typd&q=%23hohochallenge', target="_blank")
                  span.c-text-color-pink
                    | #hohochallenge, 
                |it is very important for others to see your creation.
            li 
              .c-rule
                | The challenge only lasts 1 week, so try to publish it before the challenge is closed.
            li
              .c-rule
                a.a-subscribe(href="#subscribe")
                  span.c-text-color-pink
                    | Subscribe 
                | to receive the challenges weekly. 
                span.c-text-color-pink
                  | It's free    
            li
              .c-rule
                | Join our 
                a.a-subscribe(href="https://join.slack.com/t/hohochallente/shared_invite/enQtNDAzMTI1NzQ0MTYzLTlhZDgyMWQ1NWZhYjEwMjlmZjY2NjA2YzU3YjY3MjhmZWU1NWRkZWMxMzhlOTE4NTY3OGY3MGI5NzFlOTVmMWQ")
                  span.c-text-color-pink
                    | #slack  
        




  .u-height--100
    .u-height--100.u-1-of-1
      .o-wrapper.u-height--100.u-max-width--1024
        .c-title.c-title--small
